ansition-transform hover:after:scale-x-100 hover:after:origin-bottom-left\" href=\"/#areas-we-serve\">Areas We Serve</a><a class=\"hover:text-white hover:text-shadow transition-all relative after:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] after:absolute after:w-full after:scale-x-0 after:h-0.5 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:bg-accent-400 after:origin-bottom-right after:transition-transform hover:after:scale-x-100 hover:after:origin-bottom-left\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"hover:text-white hover:text-shadow transition-all relative after:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] after:absolute after:w-full after:scale-x-0 after:h-0.5 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:bg-accent-400 after:origin-bottom-right after:transition-transform hover:after:scale-x-100 hover:after:origin-bottom-left\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center space-x-3 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] group cursor-pointer hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)] transition-shadow\"><span class=\"text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-center\">📞</span><div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-surface-500 font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest\">Need Help? Talk to Experts</div><a href=\"tel:614-926-0787\" class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-brand-900 hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors\">614-926-0787</a></div></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-brand-50 hover:text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Menu\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-[#fcfafb] text-gray-900 min-h-screen\"><section class=\"relative pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0d1b2a] overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-end min-h-[450px]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0\"><img src=\"/images/blog-5.jpg\" alt=\"5 Signs You Need an Emergency Exterminator\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0d1b2a]/60 via-[#0d1b2a]/80 to-[#0d1b2a]/95\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full\"><div class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#ff7340] text-white text-xs font-bold rounded uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Pest Control</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight max-w-4xl leading-tight\">5 Signs You Need an Emergency Exterminator</h1><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-[#ff7340]\">📅</span>2026-06-02</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-[#ff7340]\">⏱️</span>5 min read</span></div></div></section><div class=\"bg-[#f5f5f5] py-3 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 text-sm\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 overflow-x-auto whitespace-nowrap\"><a class=\"hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a><span>›</span><a class=\"hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><span>›</span><span class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900 truncate\">5 Signs You Need an Emergency Exterminator</span></div></div><section class=\"py-16 px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-8\"><article class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 prose-headings:text-[#0d1b2a] prose-a:text-[#ff7340]\"><p>Some pest problems can wait for a scheduled appointment, but others require immediate attention. Here are five signs you shouldn't ignore.</p><h2>1. Daytime Activity</h2><p>Most pests are nocturnal. If you see rodents, roaches, or bed bugs out in the open during the day, it usually indicates a severe infestation where hiding spaces are overcrowded.</p><h2>2. Property Damage</h2><p>Chewed wires, gnawed furniture, or hollow-sounding wood are signs that pests are actively destroying your property.</p><h2>3. Unusual Smells</h2><p>A musty odor can indicate mice or roaches, while a sweet, rotting smell might be bed bugs.</p><h2>4. Health Concerns</h2><p>If anyone in your household is experiencing unexplained bites, asthma flare-ups, or allergy symptoms, pests could be the culprit.</p><h2>5. Rapid Reproduction</h2><p>Pests like fleas and bed bugs multiply incredibly fast. A small problem today can become a nightmare tomorrow.</p></article><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center py-8 border-y border-gray-200 mt-16\"><a class=\"text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors flex items-center gap-2\" href=\"/blog\"><span class=\"text-lg\">←</span> Back to Blog</a></div><div class=\"mt-12\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#0d1b2a] mb-2\">Leave a Reply</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6\">Your email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *</p><form class=\"space-y-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Comment *</label><textarea rows=\"6\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 focus:border-[#ff7340] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#ff7340] focus:outline-none transition-colors\" required=\"\"></textarea></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Name *</label><input type=\"text\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 focus:border-[#ff7340] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#ff7340] focus:outline-none transition-colors\" required=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Email *</label><input type=\"email\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 focus:border-[#ff7340] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#ff7340] focus:outline-none transition-colors\" required=\"\"/></div></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"bg-[#ff7340] hover:bg-[#e66633] text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg shadow-sm transition-colors\">Post Comment</button></form></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-4 space-y-8\"><div class=\"bg-[#f5f5f5] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-wide text-sm uppercase\">Search</h3><div class=\"flex\"><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Search articles...\" class=\"flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-l-lg border border-gray-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#ff7340] text-sm\"/><button class=\"bg-[#ff7340] hover:bg-[#e66633] text-white px-4 rounded-r-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-colors\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Search</span>🔍</button></div></div><div class=\"bg-[#f5f5f5] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-wide text-sm uppercase\">Recent Posts</h3><ul class=\"space-y-4\"><li class=\"border-b border-gray-200 pb-4 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><a class=\"block font-bold text-[#0d1b2a] hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors text-sm mb-1\" href=\"/blog/importance-of-regular-pest-inspections\">The Importance of Regular Pest Inspections</a><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">2026-07-15</span></li><li class=\"border-b border-gray-200 pb-4 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><a class=\"block font-bold text-[#0d1b2a] hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors text-sm mb-1\" href=\"/blog/how-to-prevent-bed-bugs-while-traveling\">How to Prevent Bed Bugs While Traveling</a><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-500\">2026-07-10</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] rounded-2xl p-8 text-white relative overflow-hidden shadow-xl\"><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"font-extrabold text-2xl mb-2 text-white tracking-tight\">Need Help?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Have questions? We&#x27;re here to help 24/7!</p><a href=\"tel:614-926-0787\" class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-lg font-bold text-white hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors group\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📞</span>614-926-0787</a></div