border-gray-200 text-sm\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 overflow-x-auto whitespace-nowrap\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L7\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"className\":\"hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"›\"}],[\"$\",\"$L7\",null,{\"href\":\"/blog\",\"className\":\"hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors\",\"children\":\"Blog\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"›\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-gray-900 truncate\",\"children\":\"5 Signs You Need an Emergency Exterminator\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"py-16 px-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"lg:col-span-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"article\",null,{\"className\":\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 prose-headings:text-[#0d1b2a] prose-a:text-[#ff7340]\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"<p>Some pest problems can wait for a scheduled appointment, but others require immediate attention. Here are five signs you shouldn't ignore.</p><h2>1. Daytime Activity</h2><p>Most pests are nocturnal. If you see rodents, roaches, or bed bugs out in the open during the day, it usually indicates a severe infestation where hiding spaces are overcrowded.</p><h2>2. Property Damage</h2><p>Chewed wires, gnawed furniture, or hollow-sounding wood are signs that pests are actively destroying your property.</p><h2>3. Unusual Smells</h2><p>A musty odor can indicate mice or roaches, while a sweet, rotting smell might be bed bugs.</p><h2>4. Health Concerns</h2><p>If anyone in your household is experiencing unexplained bites, asthma flare-ups, or allergy symptoms, pests could be the culprit.</p><h2>5. Rapid Reproduction</h2><p>Pests like fleas and bed bugs multiply incredibly fast. A small problem today can become a nightmare tomorrow.</p>\"}}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex justify-between items-center py-8 border-y border-gray-200 mt-16\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L7\",null,{\"href\":\"/blog\",\"className\":\"text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-[#ff7340] transition-colors flex items-center gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg\",\"children\":\"←\"}],\" Back to Blog\"]}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#0d1b2a] mb-2\",\"children\":\"Leave a Reply\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6\",\"children\":\"Your email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *\"}],[\"$\",\"form\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"label\",null,{\"className\":\"block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\",\"children\":\"Comment *\"}],[\"$\",\"textarea\",null,{\"rows\":6,\"className\":\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 focus:border-[#ff7340] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#ff7340] focus:outline-none transition-colors\",\"required\":true}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"label\",null,{\"className\":\"block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\",\"children\":\"Name *\"}],[\"$\",\"input\",null,{\"type\":\"text\",\"className\":\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 focus:border-[#ff7340] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#ff7340] focus:outline-none transition-colors\",\"required\":true}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"label\",null,{\"className\":\"block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\",\"children\":\"Email *\"}],[\"$\",\"input\",null,{\"type\":\"email\",\"className\":\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 focus:border-[#ff7340] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#ff7340] focus:outline-none transition-colors\",\"